<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Secure Your Account ‚Äî Morti Projects</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            color: #333; background: #f7f8fc; min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        }
        .prompt-card {
            background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 48px 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            max-width: 480px; width: 100%; margin: 20px; text-align: center;
        }
        .shield { font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .prompt-card h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .prompt-card p { font-size: 1rem; color: #718096; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .benefits {
            text-align: left; background: #f0fff4; border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 28px;
        }
        .benefits li {
            list-style: none; font-size: 0.92rem; color: #276749; padding: 6px 0;
            padding-left: 24px; position: relative; line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .benefits li::before {
            content: '‚úì'; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: 700; color: #10b981;
        }
        .btn-setup {
            display: block; width: 100%; padding: 14px; border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; border: none; cursor: pointer;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2); color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(102,126,234,0.4);
            transition: all 0.25s; text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .btn-setup:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102,126,234,0.5); }
        .skip-link {
            display: block; padding: 12px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600;
            color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 10px; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .skip-link:hover { border-color: #667eea; background: #f7f8fc; }
        .note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #a0aec0; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="prompt-card">
    <div class="shield">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
    <h1>Protect Your Account</h1>
    <p>Two-factor authentication (2FA) adds an extra layer of security. It only takes a minute to set up.</p>

    <ul class="benefits">
        <li>Prevents unauthorised access even if your password is compromised</li>
        <li>Uses your phone as a second verification step</li>
        <li>Works with Google Authenticator, Authy, or any TOTP app</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="/profile/mfa/setup" class="btn-setup">Set Up 2FA Now</a>
    <a href="<%= user.role === 'admin' ? '/admin' : '/dashboard' %>" class="skip-link">Skip for Now ‚Üí</a>

    <p class="note">You can always enable 2FA later from your Profile settings.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
